#
# This code is based on the version generated by NVIDIA to explore 
# launching CUDA kernels under the RAJA layer without directly programming
# to CUDA in the LULESH code.  It only differs from the NVIDIA version by
# using the CUDA features added to RAJA.
#

##
## To build and run on LLNL systems...
##

> ./buildtests

# To run CilkPlus tests, you will need to set the CILK_NWORKERS environment
# variable.  Unlike OpenMP, it will not deafult to the number of cores
# available.

> srun -N 1 -p pdebug --exclusive time ./CPUtraversal-test.exe
> srun -N 1 -p pdebug --exclusive time ./CPUreduce-test.exe
